review_title: Good looking but gets loose very fast
reviews: These are nice looking bandana tubes and can be used for outdoor, hiking, fishing, etc., to cover the face and neck from insects. But they get loose quite fast and slip easily. Also on warm days they become quite hot and difficult to have them on for longer period of time. I think these are more suitable for other usages such as wrist or hair band rather than face and neck cover.
product_name: 9PCS Magic Scarf, Seamless Bandanas Tube, Headband

review_title: Most of the bandanas are nice colors and interesting patterns
reviews: Most of the bandanas are nice colors and interesting patterns, only a couple of them are a little so so but I'm sure they will all get used. The fabric is very thin and stretchy but provides good coverage.
